// STRESS 12: variable shadowing + redeclaration patterns
Create a console application.

Make a function called inc(int x) that returns an int:
    set x = x + 1
    return x

When the program starts:
    set counter = 0
    set counter = counter + 1
    set counter = counter + 1
    set counter = counter + 1
    print counter
    call inc(10)
    set msg = "before"
    set msg = "after"
    print msg
